examples.title: Run generation
examples.code:
codo = require 'codo'

file = (filename, content) ->
  console.log "New file %s with content %s", filename, content

done = (err) ->
  if err
    console.log "Cannot generate documentation:", err
  else
    console.log "Documentation generated"

codo.run file, done
